*********************************************************
APPLICATIONS	
*********************************************************

NAME		: SampleHelloWorld	
DESCRIPTION	: This is a sample shell application that will print "Sample Hello World!!" to the UEFI Console based on PCD setting.

NAME		: SampleCommandLineApplication
DESCRIPTION	: This is a sample shell application that accepts command line arguments and prints arguments count and arguments

NAME		: SampleDxeApplication
DESCRIPTION	: Sample UEFI Application reference which access DXE services using Protocol

*********************************************************
DXE DRIVER	
*********************************************************

NAME		: SampleDxe	
DESCRIPTION	: Sample DXE DRIVER which exports services by installing protocol


*********************************************************
Update Conf/target.txt
*********************************************************
ACTIVE_PLATFORM       = OvmfPkg/OvmfPkgX64.dsc
TARGET_ARCH           = X64
TOOL_CHAIN_TAG        = GCC5

*********************************************************
BUILD and SETUP FILES FOR SIMULATION
*********************************************************

1. build -p OvmfPkg/OvmfPkgX64.dsc -> Builds OVMF.fd
2. build -p SampleModulePkg/SampleModulePkg.dsc -> Builds all UEFI applications
3. cp Build/OvmfX64/DEBUG_GCC5/FV/OVMF.fd ~/QEMU/bios.bin
4. cp Build/SampleModulePkg/DEBUG_GCC5/X64/*.efi ../QEMU/HDA/

*********************************************************
QEMU SIMULATION COMMANDS
*********************************************************

qemu-system-x86_64 -L . --bios bios.bin -net none -hda fat:rw:HDA -serial stdio
